{
  "stem": "182.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "In the middle, there was on one side a latrine, on the other side the-- the wash room.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And one barrack was like an infirmary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Work, we didn't do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "We just had to lay on this thing, on this-- these beds.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And we were counted, and we were selected from time to time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "They-- they made you take off your clothes, and if they saw that, you know, women have kind of stretch marks, or stretched out stomachs, indicating that they already had babies or so, without any question they were led away, and we didn't know where.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] and these Slovak and Polish girls who were there already many years, they used to tell us, because the Germans told some people they're gonna-- there is a selection for work.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And these Polish girls told us that, don't believe that, because there is no work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "The only way you go out from here is up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And then we saw the belching of the smoke and the terrible stench, and we put two and two together.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "That maybe there is more to it that-- than we know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And that especially-- and that-- that these-- these Aufseherin, what they were called, the ones who-- Aufseherin is actually looking over.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the-- the barrack, the ones that they liked, they tried to keep that they shouldn't go away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they liked me also, because they liked my mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- we stayed in Auschwitz for six months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I really was lucky, because I was never hit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was never-- I never saw a dead person while I was there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I heard, but I didn't go to look, that there were some, mainly mothers, who lost babies.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they would scream at night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
